Berwyn, in the heart of Beautiful Berwyn this spacious 2 bedroom 2 baths 3rd floor apartment is available.  May 1, 2021.  This apartment is full of natural sunlight with sky lights.  The flooring is new and the kitchen is completely updated with new stainless steel appliances, and granite counter tops and a new sink.  Both bedrooms are large enough to accommodate your queen beds.  There is a master bath with shower and a full bath with a tub.  The closets are spacious.  Sunny natural lightening will brighten your day.  Efficient heat and flexicore building creates a sound proof unit.  You have central AC to keep you cool in the summer days.  The balcony off the living room overs a place to relax. <br>
<br>
Off street parking on paved lot in back. Shared laundry<br>
<br>
This location is a commuters dream!  Walk 5 blocks to Metra BNSF and be downtown to Unions Station in 26 minutes.  Convenient to Eisenhower expressway (I 290), Stevenson expressway (I 55) via Harlem Ave. <br>
<br>
Local hospitals near by: Loyola and MacNeal.  <br>
Convenient shopping is just 5 to 10 minutes away at Riverside Shopping with a Costco close by as well.<br>
Financials: Rent $1650<br>
Move in fee: $650<br>
Credit check: $25.00<br>
